{"tid":2333041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Facebook 刊報狂轟Apple iOS 14私隱措施損害廣告收入，不排除將來會收費","createTime":"2020-12-20T05:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T10:20:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8ebe735a9d7d8bf3253fd91a4667aeba5d8c72","tid":2333041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"據報導，Facebook 近日連續二天在《華爾街日報》、《紐約時報》和《華盛頓郵報》等刊登整版廣告，再次對 Apple 發起猛烈抨擊，針對 Apple 最近推出的 iOS 14 隱私措施表達了更多的批評。該措施將要求用家同意為個性化廣告目的追踪其活動，Facebook 希望歐盟旨在限制美國大型公司的新規草案能為該公司設定界限。此舉引發了 Apple 與 Facebook 之間的爭端。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 和其他通過賣廣告來獲取收入的公司都曾表示，這一功能將損害開發者、小企業甚至整個互聯網的利益。但反過來也有損 Apple 自己的利益。而 Apple 一方卻反擊稱：「如果你的商業模式是侵入性追踪，就會傾向於不歡迎透明度和客戶選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n對於 Apple 新的隱私措施，Facebook 表示，此舉或<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>令很多應用和網站將不得不開始收取訂閱費</strong></span>，或者增加更多的應用內購功能來維持生計，令到互聯網「變得更加昂貴」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2020/12/19/facebook-runs-apple-vs-free-internet-ad/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2020%2F12%2F19%2Ffacebook-runs-apple-vs-free-internet-ad%2F&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=6dcabe39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2020/12/19/facebook-runs-apple-vs-free-internet-ad/</a>"},{"pid":"639e2214ad2f37d4289c1924e33dde25b60a7617","tid":2333041,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03daeddca3425a9e3bde4eea047f75637c418b9f","tid":2333041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit